# CVS Playground

Playground for new technologies like bs4, sass..

### Prerequisites

After cloning this to your folder, you will need to run with any server type application like, MAMP, XAMPP on localhost or 127.0.0.1.

### Installing

For changing sass and javascript files you need to do these steps:

After starting MAMP or XAMPP on localhost you should go to folder directory where you stored index.html and run:

```
npm install
```

And after that

```
gulp watch
```

in case you are missing some of gulp dependencies:

```
npm install --save-dev gulp gulp-jshint js-hint gulp-sass gulp-clean-css gulp-concat gulp-uglify gulp-rename
```

